Privacy policy: Finder BLE App
	
	Finder BLE - Finder BLE with your privacy in mind, so we do not collect personally identifiable information 
	about you. In other words, we use your camera for scan QR-Code. 
	

	Permission requests:
	In Finder BLE, the app requests some sensitive permissions to make functions of application work properly:
	
	Permission CAMERA: To decode QR code and barcode, this is main feature of the app.
	Permission STORAGE: To download your generated barcode to local storage.
	

	The App DOES NOT collect your any information.
	
	Changes to This Privacy Policy:
	I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. 
	I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after 
	they are posted on this page.
	

	Contact Us:
	If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me.
